<td>500+ M<sup id="cite_ref-Es2009_14-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Es2009-14"><span>[</span>14<span>]</span></a></sup><sup class="noprint Inline-Template" style="white-space:nowrap;">[<i><a href="Wikipedia_Disputed_statement" title="Wikipedia:Disputed statement" class="mw-redirect"><span title="The material in the vicinity of this tag may not be factual or accurate from July 2012">dubious</span></a> <span class="metadata">– <a href="Talk_World_language#Dubious" title="Talk:World language">discuss</a></span></i>]</sup></td>
