rias-Culturales/Noticias/qel-espanol-es-actualmente-la-lengua-comun-de-casi-500-millones-de-personas-y-la-lengua-oficial-de-21-paisesq.htmlelintercultural.net">[2]</a>) ,Feu Rosa - Spanish in Mercosur (<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://congresosdelalengua.es/valladolid/ponencias/unidad_diversidad_del_espanol/5_espanol_y_portugues/rosa_f.htm">congresosdelalengua.es</a>),<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.elpais.com/articulo/carreras/capital/humano/500/millones/razones/saber/espanol/elpepueconeg/20100124elpnegser_4/Tes">elpais.com</a>,<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.eumed.net/rev/cccss/05/jrz.htm">eumed.net</a>,<a rel="nofollow" class="external autonumber" href="http://www.efeamerica.com/309_hispanic-world/879407_spain-s-king-praises-nobel-winning-vargas-llosa.htmlefeamerica.com">[3]</a>,<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.babel-linguistics.com/idiomas.htm">babel-linguistics.com</a>.</span></li>
